OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781348571
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,FHarry Styles fans have been queuing
OL,7,Ffor more than 24 hours to get a chance
OL,8,Fto see the singer up close.
OL,10,FThe former One Direction star, 32,
OL,11,Fwill kick off his 12-night residency
OL,12,Fat London's Wembley Stadium on Friday.
OL,14,FIt follows the release of his fourth
OL,15,Fsolo album, Kiss All The Time. Disco,
OL,16,FOccasionally, which was released in
OL,17,FMarch.
OL,19,FAlthough there had initially been six
OL,20,Fshows planned for London, huge demand
OL,21,Fsaw them being doubled to 12.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
