OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,FAhead of the first concert, Press
OL,7,FAssociation spoke to several fans who
OL,8,Fhad arrived at the venue hours ahead
OL,9,Fof time to secure the best seats
OL,10,Fpossible.
OL,12,FKira, 18, and Alicia, 19, live in
OL,13,FWembley but started lining up at the
OL,14,Fstadium around 6am on Thursday.
OL,16,F"We've got standing, so we want to get
OL,17,Fbarricade, so we lined up and got a
OL,18,Fnumber," Kira said.
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
