OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,FAlthough fans have been discouraged
OL,7,Ffrom camping there overnight, an
OL,8,Funofficial queue formed hours before.
OL,10,F"The queue kind of works where
OL,11,Feveryone who's there previously, you
OL,12,Fkind of get to know each other, and
OL,13,Fthen it turns into like an official
OL,14,Fqueue, and obviously you've got your
OL,15,Ffriends, so you can just be like, 'can
OL,16,Fwe go get changed and do our make-up
OL,17,Fand get ready?', and that's the basis
OL,18,Fof it really," Kira added.
OL,26,@rD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781348571
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,FThe pair added that the goal was to
OL,7,Fget in early and secure a spot at the
OL,8,Fbarricade.
OL,10,FAlicia said: "We're very much concert
OL,11,Fpeople, and being in the front, I feel
OL,12,Flike we get to experience those
OL,13,Fmemories kind of really up close
OL,14,Frather than seeing it in a video or
OL,15,Fsomething like that, like it feels
OL,16,Flike you're actually living it.
OL,26,@rD@NOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781348571
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,F"For me personally, when I go to a
OL,7,Fconcert, I kind of black out a little
OL,8,Fbit, and in that moment when the
OL,9,Fartist is right in front of you,
OL,10,Fespecially Harry, because he means so
OL,11,Fmuch to me, it's massive and I know I
OL,12,Fwill never forget it."
OL,14,FElla, 21, arrived from Liverpool on
OL,15,FThursday and stayed up all night in
OL,16,Fthe queue, an experience she said was
OL,17,F"not too bad".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@VO]yD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781348571
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,F"I met people that I've met in
OL,7,Fprevious queues before, so it's quite
OL,8,Ffun. It's like a fun little sleepover,
OL,9,Fa girly sleepover," she said.
OL,11,F"I tried to go to sleep, but I am just
OL,12,Ftoo excited, so I stayed awake all
OL,13,Fnight. I might get some sleep before I
OL,14,Fgo into the stadium, but wasn't too
OL,15,Fbad overall."
OL,17,FElla said that everyone in the queue
OL,18,Fwas "really friendly" and "respected
OL,19,Fthe process".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@SO]sD@AOUwD@MO]zD@EOUzD@UO]zD@
OL,26,A[OU{D@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781348571
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,F"It doesn't work without the fans. If
OL,7,Feveryone gets on, it just makes
OL,8,Feverything easier."
OL,10,FShe went on to share that she would be
OL,11,Fseeing Styles five times, calling it a
OL,12,F"dream come true".
OL,14,F"I saw him on his last tour and it's
OL,15,Fjust amazing to be here again. It's so
OL,16,Fsurreal."
OL,18,FMany of Styles's fans have spent
OL,19,Fhundreds ` or even thousands ` to see
OL,20,Fhim on this tour.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@SO]tD@AOUtD@QO]vD@AOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
