CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781348571
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,FRosie, 23, from Bolton, secured VIP
OL,7,Ftickets that set her back around #900.
OL,9,F"When you tell people how much you've
OL,10,Fpaid, they think you're stupid, but
OL,11,Funless you've been here and you know
OL,12,Fwhat it feels like, then you wouldn't
OL,13,Funderstand," she said.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
