FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781348571
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,F"I think there's a mutual
OL,7,Funderstanding of Harry and his fans,
OL,8,Fand I feel like within the fans as
OL,9,Fwell, that you're meeting different
OL,10,Fpeople that are completely different
OL,11,Fto you, that on a normal day you
OL,12,Fprobably wouldn't really have anything
OL,13,Fin common with them, but I feel like
OL,14,Feveryone has this sense of like coming
OL,15,Ftogether as soon as you get here,
OL,16,Flike, 'oh, we've all got Harry in
OL,17,Fcommon', and I think that's why it's
OL,18,Fjust such a good vibe."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
