CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781348571
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,FMeg and Katie, both aged 27 and from
OL,7,FSt Helens, estimate they've each spent
OL,8,F"easily" over #1,000 each to see
OL,9,FStyles too.
OL,11,FHowever, they defended the cost,
OL,12,Fsaying it felt like a "nostalgic"
OL,13,Fexperience.
OL,15,F"We've been doing this since we were
OL,16,F11 or 12 ` we've got to keep going
OL,17,Fbecause we were big One Direction fans
OL,18,Fback in the day," they said.
OL,20,FOther fans estimated they'd spent up
OL,21,Fto #4,000 each as well.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@HO]tD@WOUtD@aO]wD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
