CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781348571
OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,FMichael, 22, is originally from
OL,7,FLincolnshire but now lives in Wembley.
OL,9,FHe called Styles his "favourite
OL,10,Fartist" and said his music "has got me
OL,11,Fthrough everything".
OL,13,F"I struggle a little bit with anxiety,
OL,14,Fand I feel that his music allows me to
OL,15,Ffeel I can be myself, and I feel like
OL,16,Fhis lyrics are quite a comfort and
OL,17,Fshow you can be yourself no matter
OL,18,Fwhat you are going through, or who you
OL,19,Fare, how old you are, or your race,
OL,20,Fgender or sexuality," he said.
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@GO]rD@\OUsD@SO]uD@AOU|D@UO]
