OL,3,CHarry Styles fans queue overnight
OL,4,Cahead of Wembley residency
OL,6,FAfter his London residency, Styles
OL,7,Fwill hold the record for the most
OL,8,Fperformances by any artist in a single
OL,9,Fyear at Wembley Stadium ` surpassing
OL,10,FColdplay's 10-night run last summer.
